#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced &sheets;"
msgstr "Napredni  &sheets;"

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid "Series"
msgstr "Serije"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When constructing a spreadsheet you often need to include a series of "
"values, such as 10, 11, 12..., in a row or column. There are several ways "
"you can do this in &sheets;."
msgstr ""
"Ko sestavljate preglednico, morate v vrstico ali stolpec pogosto vključiti "
"zaporedje vrednosti, kot so 10, 11, 12 .... V &sheets; lahko to storite na "
"več načinov."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For a simple short series such as 5, 6, 7, 8... the <quote>Drag and Copy </"
"quote> method is the simplest. Enter the starting value into the starting "
"cell and the next value of the series into an adjacent cell. Then select "
"both cells and move the mouse pointer so that it is over the small square at "
"the bottom right corner; the cursor will change to a diagonal double headed "
"arrow. Then hold the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> mouse button down while "
"you drag the cells down or across as needed."
msgstr ""
"Za preprosto kratko zaporedje kot je 5, 6, 7, 8 ... je najpreprostejša "
"metoda <quote>povleci in kopiraj </quote>. Vnesite začetno vrednost v "
"začetno celico in naslednjo vrednost niza v sosednjo celico. Nato izberite "
"obe celici in premaknite kazalec miške tako, da je nad majhnim kvadratom v "
"spodnjem desnem kotu; kazalec se bo spremenil v diagonalno dvosmerno "
"puščico. Nato držite pritisnjen <mousebutton>levi</mousebutton> gumb miške, "
"medtem ko po potrebi vlečete celice navzdol ali čez."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The step size is calculated as the difference between the two starting "
"values that you have entered. For example if you enter <userinput>4</"
"userinput> into cell A1 and <userinput>3.5</userinput> into A2 then select "
"both cells and Drag and Copy them down, the step size will be the value in "
"A2 minus the value in A1, -0.5 in this case so you will get the series 4, "
"3.5, 3, 2.5, 2..."
msgstr ""
"Velikost koraka se izračuna kot razlika med dvema začetnima vrednostma, ki "
"ste ju vnesli. Če na primer vnesete <userinput>4</userinput> v celico A1 in "
"<userinput>3.5</userinput> v celico A2, nato izberete obe celici ter ju "
"povlecite in kopirajte navzdol, bo velikost koraka enaka vrednosti v A2 "
"minus vrednost v A1, v tem primeru -0,5, tako da boste dobili zaporedje 4, "
"3,5, 3, 2,5, 2 ..."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>Drag and Copy</quote> method will even cope with series where the "
"step value is not a constant value but is itself a series. So that if you "
"start with 1, 3, 4, 6 Drag and Copy will extend it to 1, 3, 4, 6, 7, 9, 10, "
"12..., the step value in this example being the series 2, 1, 2, 1..."
msgstr ""
"Metoda <quote>Povleci in kopiraj</quote> bo kos celo zaporedjem, kjer "
"vrednost koraka ni konstantna vrednost, ampak je sama niz. Torej, če začnete "
"z 1, 3, 4, 6, ga bo funkcija povleci in kopiraj razširila na 1, 3, 4, 6, 7, "
"9, 10, 12 ..., pri čemer je vrednost koraka v tem primeru zaporedje 2, 1, 2, "
"1 ..."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; also recognizes some special <quote>series</quote> such as the days "
"of the week. Try entering <userinput>Friday</userinput> into a cell (note "
"the capitalization) then Drag and Copy it down. To see what special series "
"are available, and perhaps create your own, select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Custom Lists...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"&sheets; prepozna tudi nekatere posebna <quote>zaporedja</quote> kot so "
"dnevi v tednu. Poskusite vnesti <userinput>petek</userinput> v celico "
"(upoštevajte velike črke), nato pa povlecite in kopirajte navzdol. Če želite "
"videti, katera posebna zaporedja so na voljo, in morda ustvariti svojega, "
"izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Seznami po "
"meri ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select a cell and choose <guimenuitem>Series...</guimenuitem> from "
"the <guimenu>Insert</guimenu> menu you will see the <guilabel>Series</"
"guilabel> dialog box. This is useful for creating series that are too long "
"to be conveniently constructed using the Drag and Copy method, or for "
"creating geometric series such as 1, 1.5, 2.25, 3.375... where the step "
"value, 1.5 in this case, is used as a multiplier."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete celico in v meniju <guimenu>Vstavi</guimenu> izberete "
"<guimenuitem>Niz...</guimenuitem>, boste videli pogovorno okno "
"<guilabel>Niz</guilabel>. To je uporabno za ustvarjanje zaporedij, ki so "
"predolgi, da bi jih bilo priročno sestaviti z metodo povleci in kopiraj, ali "
"za ustvarjanje geometrijskih zaporedij, kot so 1, 1,5, 2,25, 3,375 ... kjer "
"se uporablja vrednost koraka, v tem primeru 1,5 kot multiplikator."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the type of series that you want is too complicated for any of the "
"previous methods, consider using a formula and Drag and Copying that. For "
"example to create a series with the values 2, 4, 16, 256... enter "
"<userinput>2</userinput> into A1, <userinput>=A1*A1</userinput> into A2, and "
"Drag and Copy cell A2 down."
msgstr ""
"Če je vrsta zaporedja, ki ga želite, preveč zapletena za katero koli od "
"prejšnjih metod, razmislite o uporabi formule ter jo povlecite in kopirajte. "
"Na primer, če želite ustvariti niz z vrednostmi 2, 4, 16, 256 ... vnesite "
"<userinput>2</userinput> v A1, <userinput>=A1*A1</userinput> v A2 ter "
"povlecite in kopirajte celico A2 navzdol."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Formulae"
msgstr "Formule"

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Built in Functions"
msgstr "Vgrajene funkcije"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; has a huge range of built in mathematical and other <link linkend="
"\"functions\">functions</link> that can be used in a formula cell. They can "
"be seen and accessed by selecting a cell then choosing "
"<guimenuitem>Function...</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Insert</guimenu> "
"menu. This brings up the <guilabel>Function</guilabel> dialog box."
msgstr ""
"&sheets; ima ogromno vgrajenih matematičnih in drugih <link linkend="
"\"functions\">funkcij</link>, ki jih je mogoče uporabiti v celici formule. "
"Ogledate si jih in do njih lahko dostopate tako, da izberete celico in nato "
"izberete <guimenuitem>Funkcija...</guimenuitem> v meniju <guimenu>Vstavi</"
"guimenu>. To prikliče pogovorno okno <guilabel>Funkcija</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the function you want to use from the listbox at the left of the "
"dialog box. The <guilabel>Help</guilabel> tab page will then display a "
"description, the return type, Syntax, Parameters, and Examples for this "
"function. In addition this page provides often links to Related Functions. "
"Then press the button with the down arrow key symbol on it to paste it into "
"the text edit box at the bottom of the dialog."
msgstr ""
"Na seznamu na levi strani pogovornega okna izberite funkcijo, ki jo želite "
"uporabiti. Stran z zavihkom <guilabel>Pomoč</guilabel> bo nato prikazala "
"opis, vrnjeno vrsto, sintakso, parametre in primere za to funkcijo. Poleg "
"tega ta stran pogosto ponuja povezave do povezanih funkcij. Nato pritisnite "
"gumb s simbolom puščične tipke navzdol, da ga prilepite v polje za urejanje "
"besedila na dnu pogovornega okna."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Parameters</guilabel> tab page will then be displayed to let "
"you enter the parameter(s) for the function you have just chosen. If you "
"want to enter an actual value for a parameter, just type it into the "
"appropriate text box in the <guilabel>Parameters</guilabel> page. To enter a "
"cell reference rather than a value, <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click on "
"the appropriate text box in the <guilabel>Parameters</guilabel> page; then "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click on the target cell in the spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
"Nato se bo prikazala stran z zavihkom <guilabel>Parametri</guilabel>, ki vam "
"bo omogočila vnos parametrov za funkcijo, ki ste jo pravkar izbrali. Če "
"želite za parameter vnesti dejansko vrednost, jo preprosto vnesite v "
"ustrezno besedilno polje na strani <guilabel>Parametri</guilabel>. Če želite "
"namesto vrednosti vnesti sklic na celico, <mousebutton>levi</mousebutton> "
"kliknite na ustrezno besedilno polje na strani <guilabel>Parametri</"
"guilabel>; nato <mousebutton>levi</mousebutton> klik na ciljno celico v "
"preglednici."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Instead of using the <guilabel>Parameters</guilabel> page, cell references "
"such as <userinput>B6</userinput> can be entered by typing them directly "
"into the edit box at the bottom of the <guilabel>Function</guilabel> dialog. "
"If a function has more than one parameter separate them with a semi-colon "
"(<keysym>;</keysym>)."
msgstr ""
"Namesto uporabe strani <guilabel>Parametri</guilabel> lahko sklice na "
"celice, kot je <userinput>B6</userinput>, vnesete tako, da jih vnesete "
"neposredno v polje za urejanje na dnu <guilabel>Funkcije</guilabel> dialog. "
"Če ima funkcija več kot en parameter, jih ločite s podpičjem (<keysym>;</"
"keysym>)."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> button will insert the function into "
"the current cell and close the <guilabel>Function</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Če pritisnete gumb <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>, boste funkcijo vstavili v "
"trenutno celico in zaprli pogovorno okno <guilabel>Funkcija</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can of course do without the <guilabel>Function</guilabel> dialog and "
"simply type the complete expression into the main text entry box in the "
"<guilabel>Cell Editor</guilabel> tool options. Function names are not case "
"sensitive. Do not forget that all expressions must start with an <keysym>=</"
"keysym> symbol."
msgstr ""
"Seveda lahko storite brez pogovornega okna <guilabel>Funkcija</guilabel> in "
"preprosto vnesete celoten izraz v glavno polje za vnos besedila v možnostih "
"orodja <guilabel>Urejevalnik celic</guilabel>. Imena funkcij ne razlikujejo "
"med velikimi in malimi črkami. Ne pozabite, da se morajo vsi izrazi začeti s "
"simbolom <keysym>=</keysym>."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Logical Comparisons"
msgstr "Logične primerjave"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Logical functions such as IF(), AND(), OR() take parameters which have the "
"logical (boolean) values True or False. This type of value can be produced "
"by other logical functions such as ISEVEN() or by the comparison of values "
"in spreadsheet cells using the comparison expressions given in the following "
"table."
msgstr ""
"Logične funkcije, kot so IF(), AND(), OR(), sprejmejo parametre, ki imajo "
"logične (logične) vrednosti True ali False. To vrsto vrednosti lahko "
"ustvarijo druge logične funkcije, kot je ISEVEN(), ali primerjava vrednosti "
"v celicah preglednice z uporabo primerjalnih izrazov, podanih v naslednji "
"tabeli."

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid "Expression"
msgstr "Izraz"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example"
msgstr "Primer"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keysym>=</keysym><keysym>=</keysym>"
msgstr "<keysym>=</keysym><keysym>=</keysym>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "Is equal to"
msgstr "Je enako"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>A2==B3</userinput> is True if the value in A2 is equal to the "
"value in B3"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>A2==B3</userinput> je True, če je vrednost v A2 enaka vrednosti v "
"B3"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keysym>!</keysym><keysym>=</keysym>"
msgstr "<keysym>!</keysym><keysym>=</keysym>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:129 advanced.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "Is not equal to"
msgstr "Ni enako"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>A2!=B3</userinput> is True if the value in A2 is not equal to the "
"value in B3"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>A2!=B3</userinput> je True, če vrednost v A2 ni enaka vrednosti v "
"B3"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keysym>&lt;</keysym><keysym>&gt;</keysym>"
msgstr "<keysym>&lt;</keysym><keysym>&gt;</keysym>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "Same as <userinput>A2!=B3</userinput>"
msgstr "Enako kot <userinput>A2!=B3</userinput>"

#. Tag: keysym
#: advanced.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;"
msgstr "&lt;"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "Is less than"
msgstr "Je manj kot"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>A2&lt;B3</userinput> is True if the value in A2 is less than the "
"value in B3"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>A2&lt;B3</userinput> je True, če je vrednost v A2 manjša od "
"vrednosti v B3"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keysym>&lt;</keysym><keysym>=</keysym>"
msgstr "<keysym>&lt;</keysym><keysym>=</keysym>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid "Is less than or equal to"
msgstr "Je manjše ali enako"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>A2&lt;=B3</userinput> is True if the value in A2 is less than or "
"equal to the value in B3"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>A2&lt;=B3</userinput> je True, če je vrednost v A2 manjša ali "
"enaka vrednosti v B3"

#. Tag: keysym
#: advanced.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "&gt;"
msgstr "&gt;"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "Is greater than"
msgstr "Je večje od"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>A2&gt;B3</userinput> is True if the value in A2 is greater than "
"the value in B3"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>A2&gt;B3</userinput> je True, če je vrednost v A2 večja od "
"vrednosti v B3"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keysym>&gt;</keysym><keysym>=</keysym>"
msgstr "<keysym>&gt;</keysym><keysym>=</keysym>"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "Is greater than or equal to"
msgstr "Je večje ali enako"

#. Tag: entry
#: advanced.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>A2&gt;=B3</userinput> is True if the value A2 is greater than or "
"equal to the value in B3"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>A2&gt;=B3</userinput> je True, če je vrednost A2 večja ali enaka "
"vrednosti v B3"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Thus if you enter <userinput>=IF(B3&gt;B1;\"BIGGER\";\"\")</userinput> into "
"a cell it will display BIGGER if the value in B3 is greater than that in B1, "
"otherwise the cell will show nothing."
msgstr ""
"Če torej v celico vnesete <userinput>=IF(B3&gt;B1;\"BIGGER\";\"\")</"
"userinput>, bo prikazano VEČJE, če je vrednost v B3 večja od tiste v B1, "
"sicer celica ne bo prikazala ničesar ."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "Absolute Cell References"
msgstr "Absolutne reference celic"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a formula contains a cell reference that reference will normally be "
"changed when the cell is copied to another part of the worksheet. To prevent "
"this behavior put a <keysym>$</keysym> symbol before the column letter, row "
"number or both."
msgstr ""
"Če formula vsebuje sklic na celico, se ta sklic običajno spremeni, ko je "
"celica kopirana v drug del delovnega lista. Če želite preprečiti to vedenje, "
"postavite simbol <keysym>$</keysym> pred črko stolpca, številko vrstice ali "
"oboje."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If A1 contains the formula <userinput>=D5</userinput> then on copying the "
"cell to B2 it will become <userinput>=E6</userinput> (the normal behavior)."
msgstr ""
"Če A1 vsebuje formulo <userinput>=D5</userinput>, bo ob kopiranju celice v "
"B2 postala <userinput>=E6</userinput> (običajno vedenje)."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If A1 contains the formula <userinput>=$D5</userinput> then on copying the "
"cell to B2 it will become <userinput>=D6</userinput> (column letter not "
"changed)."
msgstr ""
"Če A1 vsebuje formulo <userinput>=$D5</userinput>, bo ob kopiranju celice v "
"B2 postala <userinput>=D6</userinput> (črka stolpca ni spremenjena)."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If A1 contains the formula <userinput>=D$5</userinput> then on copying the "
"cell to B2 it will become <userinput>=E5</userinput> (row number not "
"changed)."
msgstr ""
"Če A1 vsebuje formulo <userinput>=D$5</userinput>, bo ob kopiranju celice v "
"B2 postala <userinput>=E5</userinput> (številka vrstice ni spremenjena)."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If A1 contains the formula <userinput>=$D$5</userinput> then on copying the "
"cell to B2 it will remain as <userinput>=D5</userinput> (neither the column "
"letter nor the row number are changed)."
msgstr ""
"Če A1 vsebuje formulo <userinput>=$D$5</userinput>, bo pri kopiranju celice "
"v B2 ostala kot <userinput>=D5</userinput> (ne črka stolpca ne številka "
"vrstice se ne spremenita)."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are entering or editing a cell reference in a formula the shortcut "
"key <keysym>F4</keysym> can be used to step through these four possibilities."
msgstr ""
"Ko vnašate ali urejate sklic na celico v formuli, lahko uporabite bližnjično "
"tipko <keysym>F4</keysym> za pomikanje po teh štirih možnostih."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"namedareas\">Named cells</link> can be used in a similar way "
"to include a unchanging cell reference in a formula."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"namedareas\">Poimenovane celice</link> je mogoče uporabiti "
"na podoben način za vključitev nespremenljivega sklica na celico v formulo."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arithmetic using Special Paste"
msgstr "Aritmetika z uporabo posebnega lepljenja"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sometimes you may want to add a single value to a number of cells, or "
"subtract a value from them, or multiply or divide them all by a single "
"value. The <guimenuitem>Special Paste...</guimenuitem> option lets you do "
"this quickly and easily."
msgstr ""
"Včasih boste morda želeli več celicam dodati eno vrednost ali od njih "
"odšteti vrednost ali jih vse pomnožiti ali deliti z eno samo vrednostjo. "
"Možnost <guimenuitem>Posebno lepljenje...</guimenuitem> vam omogoča, da to "
"storite hitro in preprosto."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First, enter the modifier value into any spare cell on your spreadsheet and "
"<guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> it. Then select the area of cells you want "
"to change, choose <guimenuitem>Special Paste...</guimenuitem> from the "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> or the context menu and select <guilabel>Addition</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Subtraction</guilabel>, <guilabel>Multiplication</"
"guilabel> or <guilabel>Division</guilabel> from the <guilabel>Operation</"
"guilabel> section of the dialog box."
msgstr ""
"Najprej vnesite vrednost modifikatorja v katero koli prosto celico v vaši "
"preglednici in jo <guimenuitem>kopirajte</guimenuitem>. Nato izberite "
"območje celic, ki jih želite spremeniti, izberite <guimenuitem>Posebno "
"lepljenje...</guimenuitem> v <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> ali kontekstnem meniju "
"in izberite <guilabel>Dodatek</guilabel>, <guilabel>Odštevanje</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Množenje</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Deljenje</guilabel> iz razdelka "
"<guilabel>Operacija</guilabel> v pogovornem oknu."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also apply different modifier values to different rows or columns of "
"the target area by copying an area containing the wanted modifiers before "
"selecting the target area and doing <guimenuitem>Special Paste...</"
"guimenuitem> For example, if you enter <userinput>5</userinput> into cell "
"A1, <userinput>10</userinput> into B1, select both cells and do a "
"<guimenuitem> Copy</guimenuitem> then <guimenuitem>Special Paste...</"
"guimenuitem> <guilabel> Addition</guilabel> into cells A10 to D15, 5 will be "
"added to A10:A15 and C10:C15, and 10 to B10:B15 and D10:D15."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite lahko tudi različne vrednosti modifikatorjev za različne vrstice "
"ali stolpce ciljnega območja, tako da kopirate območje, ki vsebuje želene "
"modifikatorje, preden izberete ciljno območje in izvedete "
"<guimenuitem>Posebno lepljenje ...</guimenuitem> Če na primer vnesete "
"<userinput>5</userinput> v celico A1, <userinput>10</userinput> v B1, "
"izberite obe celici in naredite <guimenuitem> Kopiraj</guimenuitem> nato "
"<guimenuitem>Posebno lepljenje ...</guimenuitem> <guilabel> Dodajanje</"
"guilabel> v celice A10 do D15, 5 bo dodanih v A10:A15 in C10:C15, 10 pa v "
"B10:B15 in D10:D15."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that a modifier value can be a formula as well as a simple numeric "
"value. If it is a formula then &sheets; will adjust the cell references as "
"for a normal <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> operation."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da je vrednost modifikatorja lahko tako formula kot tudi "
"preprosta številska vrednost. Če je formula, potem bo &sheets; prilagodil "
"sklice na celice kot pri običajni operaciji <guimenuitem>Prilepi</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "Array Formulas"
msgstr "Matrične formule"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; allows you to use formulas whose result is a matrix or a range of "
"values. Normally, only the first value is displayed in a cell. If you would "
"like to display the entire matrix, simply use <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Alt;&Enter;</"
"keycombo> when editing a formula, and it will be converted into an array "
"formula, occupying neighboring cells as needed."
msgstr ""
"&sheets; vam omogoča uporabo formul, katerih rezultat je matrika ali obseg "
"vrednosti. Običajno je v celici prikazana samo prva vrednost. Če želite "
"prikazati celotno matriko, pri urejanju formule preprosto uporabite "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;&Alt;&Enter;</keycombo> in ta bo pretvorjena v matrično "
"formulo, ki bo po potrebi zasedla sosednje celice."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cells that are a part of an array formula are locked for editing."
msgstr "Celice, ki so del matrične formule, so zaklenjene za urejanje."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "Goal Seeking"
msgstr "Iskanje cilja"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; can be used to solve algebraic expressions such as <emphasis> x + "
"x^2 = 4</emphasis> or <emphasis>For what value of x does x + x squared equal "
"4 ?</emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"&sheets; lahko uporabite za reševanje algebrskih izrazov, kot je <emphasis> "
"x + x^2 = 4</emphasis> ali <emphasis>Za katero vrednost x je x + x na "
"kvadrat enako 4?</emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For this example you could enter <userinput>=A2+A2*A2</userinput> into A1 "
"then either try different values in A2 until the result in A1 is as close as "
"you wish to <emphasis>4</emphasis> or, preferably, use &sheets;'s "
"<guimenuitem>Goal Seek...</guimenuitem> feature which automatically adjusts "
"the value in one cell to try to make the value in another cell as close as "
"possible to a target value."
msgstr ""
"Za ta primer bi lahko v A1 vnesli <userinput>=A2+A2*A2</userinput>, nato pa "
"bodisi poskusili z različnimi vrednostmi v A2, dokler rezultat v A1 ni tako "
"blizu <emphasis>4</emphasis>, kot želite, ali po možnosti uporabite &sheets; "
"funkcijo <guimenuitem>Iskanje cilja...</guimenuitem>, ki samodejno prilagodi "
"vrednost v eni celici, da poskuša vrednost v drugi celici čim bolj "
"približati ciljni vrednosti."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is invoked by selecting <guimenuitem>Goal Seek...</guimenuitem> from the "
"<guimenu>Data</guimenu> menu. This brings up a dialog box in which you "
"should enter the reference of the target value cell (<userinput>A1</"
"userinput> in this case) into the <guilabel>Set cell:</guilabel> box, the "
"target value itself (<userinput>4</userinput>) into the <guilabel>To value:</"
"guilabel> box and the reference of the cell that is to be changed "
"(<userinput>A2</userinput>) into the <guilabel>By changing cell:</guilabel> "
"box. Note that you need to have entered some initial value into the cell "
"that is to be changed before starting <guimenuitem>Goal Seek</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Prikličete ga tako, da izberete <guimenuitem>Iskanje cilja ...</guimenuitem> "
"v meniju <guimenu>Podatki</guimenu>. To prikliče pogovorno okno, v katerem "
"morate v polje <guilabel>Nastavi celico:</guilabel> vnesti referenco celice "
"ciljne vrednosti (<userinput>A1</userinput>), samo ciljno vrednost "
"( <userinput>4</userinput>) v polje <guilabel>Vrednost:</guilabel> in sklic "
"celice, ki jo želite spremeniti (<userinput>A2</userinput>) v polje "
"<guilabel>S spreminjanjem celica:</guilabel> polje. Upoštevajte, da morate "
"pred začetkom <guimenuitem>Iskanja cilja</guimenuitem> vnesti nekaj začetne "
"vrednosti v celico, ki jo želite spremeniti."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> button will start the calculation. "
"When it finishes and if it has found a solution press the <guibutton>OK</"
"guibutton> button to accept the result or <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> to "
"keep the original value."
msgstr ""
"S pritiskom na gumb <guibutton>V redu</guibutton> se začne izračun. Ko se "
"konča in če je našel rešitev, pritisnite gumb <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>, "
"da sprejmete rezultat, ali <guibutton>Prekliči</guibutton>, da obdržite "
"prvotno vrednost."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pivot Tables"
msgstr "Vrtilne tabele"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; can be used to construct <ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Pivot_table\">pivot tables</ulink> using the data of the current table."
msgstr ""
"&sheets; lahko uporabite za izdelavo <ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/"
"wiki/Pivot_table\">vrtilnih tabel</ulink> z uporabo podatkov trenutne tabele."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This feature can be invoked by selecting <guimenuitem>Pivot...</guimenuitem> "
"from the <guimenu>Data</guimenu> menu. Below is an example of pivot table "
"generation."
msgstr ""
"To funkcijo lahko prikličete z izbiro <guimenuitem>Vrtišče...</guimenuitem> "
"v meniju <guimenu>Podatki</guimenu>. Spodaj je primer generiranja vrtilne "
"tabele."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid "Supposing we have the following data."
msgstr "Recimo, da imamo naslednje podatke."

#. Tag: phrase
#: advanced.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Initial table"
msgstr "Začetna tabela"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"We want to create a pivot table of our choice and requirement. So we choose "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Data</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pivot...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Želimo ustvariti vrtilno tabelo po naši izbiri in zahtevah. Zato izberemo "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Podatki</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Vrtišče...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The dialog box that will appear allows user to select the source of data. "
"The data can be taken from the current worksheet or from an external source "
"like a database or <abbrev>ODS</abbrev> file."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno, ki se prikaže, omogoča uporabniku izbiro vira podatkov. "
"Podatke je mogoče vzeti iz trenutnega delovnega lista ali iz zunanjega vira, "
"kot je zbirka podatkov ali <abbrev>ODS</abbrev> datoteka."

#. Tag: phrase
#: advanced.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choosing the data source"
msgstr "Izbira vira podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here is the dialog box which allows the user to customize the pivot table. "
"The column labels in the source data are converted to labels which serve as "
"the working fields. The labels can be dragged and dropped into one of three "
"areas (<guilabel>Rows</guilabel>, <guilabel>Columns</guilabel> or "
"<guilabel>Values</guilabel>) to generate the pivot table. You can reset your "
"choices using <guibutton>Reset DnD</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj je pogovorno okno, ki uporabniku omogoča prilagajanje vrtilne tabele."
"Oznake stolpcev v izvornih podatkih se pretvorijo v oznake, ki služijo "
"kotdelovna polja. Oznake lahko povlečete in spustite v enega od trehpodročij "
"(<guilabel>Vrstice</guilabel>, <guilabel>Stolpci</guilabel> oz."
"<guilabel>Vrednosti</guilabel>), da ustvarite vrtilno tabelo. Lahko "
"ponastavite svojemožnosti z gumbom <guibutton>Ponastavi DnD</guibutton>."

#. Tag: phrase
#: advanced.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pivot table customization dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za prilagajanje vrtilne tabele"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In our example, <replaceable>Name</replaceable> is dragged to "
"<guilabel>Rows</guilabel>, <replaceable>Category</replaceable> to "
"<guilabel>Columns</guilabel>, <replaceable>Score</replaceable> to "
"<guilabel>Values</guilabel>. User defined functions like sum, average, max, "
"min, count, &etc; can be selected from the <guilabel>Select Option</"
"guilabel> list."
msgstr ""
"V našem primeru je <replaceable>Name</replaceable> povlečeno na "
"<guilabel>Vrstice</guilabel>, <replaceable>Kategorija</replaceable> do "
"<guilabel>Stolpci</guilabel>, <replaceable>Ocena</replaceable> "
"do<guilabel>Vrednosti</guilabel>. Uporabniško določene funkcije, kot so "
"vsota, povprečje, max, min, štetje itd. lahko izberete v seznamu "
"<guilabel>Izberi možnost</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Add Filter</guibutton> button can be used to open filter "
"dialog box to filter the desired data. Using this box you can define "
"multiple filters based on the column label and the relationship between them "
"(<guimenuitem>And</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Or</guimenuitem>). This "
"would allow extreme freedom to customize the output."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>Dodaj filter</guibutton> lahko uporabite za odpiranje "
"filtrapogovorno okno za filtriranje želenih podatkov. S tem poljem lahko "
"določiteveč filtrov na podlagi oznake stolpca in razmerja med njimi "
"(<guimenuitem>In</guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Ali</guimenuitem>). To bi "
"omogočilo izjemno svobodo prilagajanja izhoda."

#. Tag: phrase
#: advanced.docbook:337
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pivot table filtering dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za filtriranje vrtilne tabele"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Total Rows</guilabel> and <guilabel>Total Columns</guilabel>: "
"checking these allow automatic totalling of corresponding rows and columns "
"in the pivot table."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Skupno število vrstic</guilabel> in <guilabel>Skupno število "
"stolpcev</guilabel>: označevanje teh možnosti omogoča samodejno seštevanje "
"ustreznih vrstic in stolpcev v vrtilni tabeli."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using more than one Worksheet"
msgstr "Uporaba več kot enega delovnega lista"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start a new, empty, document with &sheets; it will create a number "
"of blank worksheets. The number of sheets it creates is determined by the "
"selected template."
msgstr ""
"Ko začnete nov, prazen dokument z &sheets; bo ustvaril številne prazne "
"delovne liste. Število listov, ki jih ustvari, je odvisno od izbrane "
"predloge."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Insert</guimenu><guimenuitem>Sheet</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> will add another sheet to the document."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Vstavi</guimenu><guimenuitem>List</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> bo dokumentu dodal še en list."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also switch between worksheets by using the <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keysym>PgDown</keysym></keycombo> to move to the next sheet, "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keysym>PgUp</keysym></keycombo> to move to "
"the previous one."
msgstr ""
"Med delovnimi listi lahko preklapljate tudi tako, da uporabite <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keysym>PgDown</keysym></keycombo> za pomik na "
"naslednji list, <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keysym >PgUp</keysym></"
"keycombo> za pomik na prejšnjega."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Worksheets are given the default names of <emphasis>Sheet1</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>Sheet2</emphasis>... You can give a sheet a different name by "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> clicking on the tab and selecting "
"<guimenuitem>Rename Sheet...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"Delovni listi imajo privzeta imena <emphasis>Sheet1</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>Sheet2</emphasis> ... Listu lahko daste drugačno ime tako, da "
"<mousebutton>desno</mousebutton> kliknete zavihek in izberete "
"<guimenuitem>Preimenuj list...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove a sheet from the document use the <guimenuitem>Remove Sheet </"
"guimenuitem> option in the context menu that pops up when you "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on the tab for the sheet you want to "
"remove."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odstraniti list iz dokumenta, uporabite možnost "
"<guimenuitem>Odstrani list </guimenuitem> v priročnem meniju, ki se prikaže, "
"ko <mousebutton>desno</mousebutton> kliknete zavihek za list, ki ga želite "
"odstraniti."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Other entries in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guisubmenu> "
"Sheet</guisubmenu></menuchoice> submenu allow you to show or hide a sheet in "
"much the same way as rows and columns can be hidden."
msgstr ""
"Drugi vnosi v podmeniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Oblika</guimenu><guisubmenu> "
"List</guisubmenu></menuchoice> vam omogočajo, da prikažete ali skrijete list "
"na približno enak način, kot se lahko skrijejo vrstice in stolpci."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want a formula in one sheet to refer to a cell in another sheet, the "
"cell reference must start with the sheet name followed by an exclamation "
"mark (<keysym>!</keysym>). For example if you enter <userinput>=Sheet2!A2 </"
"userinput> into a cell in Sheet 1, that cell will take the value from A2 of "
"Sheet2. Note that sheet names are case sensitive."
msgstr ""
"Če želite, da se formula na enem listu nanaša na celico na drugem listu, se "
"mora sklic na celico začeti z imenom lista, ki mu sledi klicaj (<keysym>!</"
"keysym>). Če na primer vnesete <userinput>=Sheet2!A2 </userinput> v celico "
"na listu 1, bo ta celica prevzela vrednost iz A2 na listu 2. Upoštevajte, da "
"imena listov razlikujejo med velikimi in malimi črkami."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid "Consolidating Data"
msgstr "Konsolidacija podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may have constructed a document containing several worksheets containing "
"similar data but for, say, different months of the year, and wish to have "
"summary sheet containing the consolidated (&eg;, sum or average) values of "
"the corresponding data items in the other sheets."
msgstr ""
"Morda ste izdelali dokument, ki vsebuje več delovnih listov s podobnimi "
"podatki, vendar za, recimo, različne mesece v letu, in želite imeti list s "
"povzetkom, ki vsebuje konsolidirane (&eg; vsoto ali povprečje) vrednosti "
"ustreznih podatkovnih postavk v drugih listih ."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This task can be made slightly easier by using the <guimenuitem> "
"Consolidate...</guimenuitem> item from the <guimenu>Data</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"To nalogo lahko nekoliko olajšate z uporabo elementa <guimenuitem> Uskladi..."
"</guimenuitem> v meniju <guimenu>Podatki</guimenu>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting this option brings up the <guilabel>Consolidate</guilabel> dialog "
"box."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete to možnost, se prikaže pogovorno okno <guilabel>Uskladi</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each of the source sheets, enter a reference to the desired data area in "
"the <guilabel>Reference:</guilabel> box. Press <guibutton>Add</guibutton> to "
"transfer it to the <guilabel>Entered references:</guilabel> box. The "
"reference should include the name of the sheet containing the source data, "
"such as <userinput>January!A1:A10</userinput>, and can be entered "
"automatically by selecting the area in the appropriate sheet."
msgstr ""
"Za vsako od izvornih listov v polje <guilabel>Sklic:</guilabel> vnesite "
"sklic na želeno podatkovno področje. Pritisnite <guibutton>Dodaj</"
"guibutton>, da ga prenesete v polje <guilabel>Vnesene reference:</guilabel>. "
"Sklic mora vključevati ime lista, ki vsebuje izvorne podatke, kot je "
"<userinput>Januar!A1:A10</userinput>, in ga je mogoče vnesti samodejno z "
"izbiro območja na ustreznem listu."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After entering the references for all of the source data sheets select the "
"cell in the target sheet where you want the top left corner of the "
"consolidated results to appear. Then choose the appropriate function from "
"the <guilabel>Function:</guilabel> combo box and press the <guibutton>OK</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Po vnosu referenc za vse izvorne podatkovne liste izberite celico na ciljnem "
"listu, kjer želite, da se prikaže zgornji levi kot konsolidiranih "
"rezultatov. Nato izberite ustrezno funkcijo v kombiniranem polju "
"<guilabel>Funkcija:</guilabel> in pritisnite gumb <guibutton>V redu</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:397
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you click the <guibutton>Details >></guibutton> in the dialog and check "
"the <guilabel>Copy data</guilabel> box the values resulting from the "
"consolidation will be placed into the target cells rather than the formulae "
"to calculate them."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete <guibutton>Podrobnosti >></guibutton> v pogovornem oknu in "
"potrdite polje <guilabel>Kopiraj podatke</guilabel>, bodo vrednosti, ki "
"izhajajo iz konsolidacije, nameščene v ciljne celice namesto v formule za "
"njihov izračun ."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inserting a Chart"
msgstr "Vstavljanje grafikona"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can insert a chart into a sheet to give a graphical view of your data."
msgstr "Grafikon lahko vstavite v list za grafični prikaz svojih podatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First enable <guilabel>Add Shape</guilabel> docker using the <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dockers</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> "
"menu item."
msgstr ""
"Najprej omogočite okence <guilabel>Dodaj obliko</guilabel> z uporabo "
"menijske postavke <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Sidrišča</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Then select the area of cells containing the data and choose "
"<guilabel>Chart</guilabel> in the <guilabel>Add Shape</guilabel>. Drag the "
"cursor across the sheet while holding the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> "
"mouse button down to define the area where you want the chart to appear, "
"there is no need to be too accurate at this stage as the chart size can "
"easily be changed at any time. When you release the mouse button a "
"<guilabel>Chart Options</guilabel> dialog box will appear."
msgstr ""
"Nato izberite območje celic, ki vsebujejo podatke, in izberite "
"<guilabel>Grafikon</guilabel> v <guilabel>Dodaj obliko</guilabel>. Povlecite "
"kazalec čez list, medtem ko držite pritisnjen <mousebutton>levi</"
"mousebutton> gumb miške, da določite območje, kjer želite, da se grafikon "
"prikaže. Na tej stopnji ni treba biti preveč natančen, saj lahko velikost "
"grafikona preprosto določite kadarkoli spremenili. Ko spustite miškino "
"tipko, se prikaže pogovorno okno <guilabel>Možnosti grafikona</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The data area is already prefilled with the selected cell range. Select the "
"first row and column as labels, check <guilabel>Data set in rows</guilabel> "
"and click the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> button. The Dialog will vanish and "
"you will see the chart embedded into the worksheet."
msgstr ""
"Podatkovno območje je že vnaprej napolnjeno z izbranim obsegom celic. "
"Izberite prvo vrstico in stolpec kot oznake, označite <guilabel>Nabor "
"podatkov v vrsticah</guilabel> in kliknite gumb <guibutton>V redu</"
"guibutton>. Pogovorno okno bo izginilo in videli boste grafikon, vdelan v "
"delovni list."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:420
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now select <guibutton>Chart Editing Tool</guibutton> from the "
"<guilabel>Tools</guilabel> docker and edit the chart properties like chart "
"type, labels and axis in the <guilabel>Chart editing</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Sedaj izberite <guibutton>Orodje za urejanje grafikonov</guibutton> v orodju "
"<guilabel>Orodja</guilabel> in uredite lastnosti grafikona, kot so vrsta "
"grafikona, oznake in os v <guilabel>Urejanje grafikona</guilabel>."

#. Tag: phrase
#: advanced.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of embedded chart"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona vdelanega grafikona"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To move, resize or even delete the embedded chart switch to the "
"<guibutton>Basic shape manipulation</guibutton> tool and click anywhere "
"within the chart area. It should now appear with a green border and with a "
"small yellow square at each corner and in the middle of each edge."
msgstr ""
"Če želite premakniti, spremeniti velikost ali celo izbrisati vdelani "
"grafikon, preklopite na orodje <guibutton>Manipulacija osnovne oblike</"
"guibutton> in kliknite kjer koli znotraj območja grafikona. Zdaj bi se moral "
"pojaviti z zeleno obrobo in z majhnim rumenim kvadratom na vsakem vogalu in "
"na sredini vsakega roba."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:438
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you move the cursor over any of the squares it should change to a double "
"headed arrow. You can resize the chart by dragging one of these squares with "
"the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> mouse button pressed. To delete the "
"chart <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on one of the squares and "
"select <guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Če kazalec premaknete čez katerega koli kvadrata, se mora spremeniti v "
"dvosmerno puščico. Velikost grafikona lahko spremenite tako, da povlečete "
"enega od teh kvadratov s pritisnjeno <mousebutton>levo</mousebutton> tipko "
"miške. Če želite izbrisati grafikon, <mousebutton>desno</mousebutton> "
"kliknite na enega od kvadratkov in izberite <guimenuitem>Izbriši</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:443
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To move the chart move the cursor into the chart. The cursor should then "
"change to a cross, press the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> mouse button "
"and you will be able to drag the chart to where you want it to be."
msgstr ""
"Če želite premakniti grafikon, premaknite kazalec na grafikon. Kazalec naj "
"se nato spremeni v križec, pritisnite <mousebutton>levi</mousebutton> gumb "
"miške in grafikon boste lahko potegnili na želeno mesto."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To restore the chart to its normal appearance simply click anywhere outside "
"of the chart area."
msgstr ""
"Če želite obnoviti običajen videz grafikona, preprosto kliknite kjer koli "
"zunaj območja grafikona."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the format of the chart itself <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> "
"click twice within the chart area. The chart <guilabel>Chart editing</"
"guilabel> should appear in the docker. You can then use these tools to "
"change the chart."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti obliko samega grafikona, <mousebutton>levo</"
"mousebutton> dvakrat kliknite znotraj območja grafikona. Grafikon "
"<guilabel>Urejanje grafikona</guilabel> bi se moral prikazati v oknu. S temi "
"orodji lahko nato spremenite grafikon."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:456
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inserting External Data"
msgstr "Vstavljanje zunanjih podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:457
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can insert data from a text file or from the clipboard into a worksheet "
"by first selecting the cell where you want the top left item of the inserted "
"data to appear, then choosing <guimenuitem>From Text File...</guimenuitem> "
"or <guimenuitem>From Clipboard...</guimenuitem> from the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Insert</guimenu><guisubmenu>External Data</guisubmenu> "
"</menuchoice> sub menu."
msgstr ""
"Podatke iz besedilne datoteke ali odložišča lahko vstavite v delovni list "
"tako, da najprej izberete celico, kjer želite, da se prikaže zgornji levi "
"element vstavljenih podatkov, nato pa izberete <guimenuitem>Iz besedilne "
"datoteke...</guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Iz odložišča ...</guimenuitem> iz "
"podmenija <menuchoice><guimenu>Vstavi</guimenu><guisubmenu>Zunanje podatke</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:463
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In both cases &sheets; will assume that the data is in <acronym>CSV</"
"acronym> form and will open a dialog box allowing you to control how the "
"data is extracted from the file or clipboard and placed into the worksheet "
"cells."
msgstr ""
"V obeh primerih &sheets; predvideva, da so podatki v obliki <acronym>CSV</"
"acronym>, in odpre pogovorno okno, ki vam omogoča nadzor nad tem, kako se "
"podatki ekstrahirajo iz datoteke ali odložišča in postavijo v celice "
"delovnega lista."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:467
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If support for it has been included in your system, &sheets; can also insert "
"data from a <acronym>SQL</acronym> database into a worksheet. This is done "
"by using the <menuchoice><guimenu>Insert</guimenu><guisubmenu> External "
"Data</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>From Database...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> "
"option."
msgstr ""
"Če je bila podpora zanj vključena v vaš sistem, &sheets; lahko tudi vstavi "
"podatke iz baze podatkov <acronym>SQL</acronym> v delovni list. To storite z "
"uporabo možnosti <menuchoice><guimenu>Vstavi</guimenu><guisubmenu> Zunanje "
"podatke</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Iz zbirke podatkov...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid "Link Cells"
msgstr "Povezovalne celice"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A spreadsheet cell can be linked to an action so that <mousebutton> left </"
"mousebutton> clicking on the cell will, for example, open your browser. To "
"make a cell act in this way select it and choose "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Insert</guimenu><guimenuitem>Link...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>. This will bring up the <guilabel>Insert Link</guilabel> dialog "
"box, which lets you choose between four types of link:"
msgstr ""
"Celico preglednice je mogoče povezati z dejanjem, tako da <mousebutton> "
"levim </mousebutton> klikom na celico na primer odpre vaš brskalnik. Če "
"želite, da celica deluje na ta način, jo izberite in izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Vstavi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Povezava...</guimenuitem> "
"</menuchoice>. To bo prikazalo pogovorno okno <guilabel>Vstavi povezavo</"
"guilabel>, v katerem lahko izbirate med štirimi vrstami povezav:"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:484
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An <guilabel>Internet</guilabel> link cell will try to open your default "
"browser at the &URL; entered in the <guilabel>Internet address:</guilabel> "
"text box of the <guilabel>Insert Link</guilabel> dialog when it is clicked. "
"This could be, for example, <userinput>http://www.calligra.org</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Internetna</guilabel> povezovalna celica bo poskušala odpreti vaš "
"privzeti brskalnik na &URL; vnesen v besedilno polje <guilabel>Internet "
"naslov:</guilabel> pogovornega okna <guilabel>Vstavi povezavo</guilabel>, ko "
"ga kliknete. To je lahko na primer <userinput>http://www.calligra.org</"
"userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on a cell containing a <guilabel>Mail</guilabel> link will open "
"your email composer using the address entered in the <guilabel>Email:</"
"guilabel> text box as the To: address. For example <userinput>anon@example."
"com</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na celico, ki vsebuje povezavo <guilabel>Pošta</guilabel>, se odpre "
"vaš urejevalnik e-pošte z uporabo naslova, vnesenega v besedilno polje "
"<guilabel>E-pošta:</guilabel> kot naslov Za:. Na primer "
"<userinput>anon@example.com</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <guilabel>File</guilabel> link cell holds the path to a file or folder, as "
"entered into the <guilabel>File location:</guilabel> text box, and will try "
"to open that file or folder with a suitable application when clicked on."
msgstr ""
"Povezavna celica <guilabel>Datoteka</guilabel> vsebuje pot do datoteke ali "
"mape, kot je vnesena v besedilno polje <guilabel>Lokacija datoteke:</"
"guilabel>, in bo poskusila odpreti to datoteko ali mapo z ustreznim "
"programom ob kliku."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Cell</guilabel> type of link cell holds a &sheets; cell "
"reference, entered in the <guilabel>Cell or Named Area</guilabel> text box. "
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> clicking on this type of link cell causes "
"&sheets;'s focus to move to the target cell."
msgstr ""
"Vrsta celice povezave <guilabel>Celica</guilabel> vsebuje sklic &sheets; na "
"celico, vneseno v besedilno polje <guilabel>Celica ali imenovano območje</"
"guilabel>. <mousebutton>Levi</mousebutton> klik na to vrsto povezovalne "
"celice povzroči, da se fokus &sheets; premakne na ciljno celico."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All four types of link cell need some suitable text to be entered into the "
"<guilabel>Text to display</guilabel> field of the <guilabel>Insert Link</"
"guilabel> dialog. This is the text that appears in the cell."
msgstr ""
"Vse štiri vrste povezovalnih celic potrebujejo ustrezno besedilo, ki ga je "
"treba vnesti v polje <guilabel>Besedilo za prikaz</guilabel> pogovornega "
"okna <guilabel>Vstavi povezavo</guilabel>. To je besedilo, ki se pojavi v "
"celici."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid "Validity Checking"
msgstr "Preverjanje veljavnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:517
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; can automatically check the validity of entered data against a "
"number of criteria, and pop up a message box if the data is invalid."
msgstr ""
"&sheets; lahko samodejno preveri veljavnost vnesenih podatkov glede na "
"številne kriterije in odpre okno s sporočilom, če so podatki neveljavni."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To enable this feature, select the cell(s) to be monitored and choose "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Data</guimenu><guimenuitem>Validity...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>. This will bring up &sheets;'s <guilabel>Validity</guilabel> "
"dialog box which has three tabbed pages."
msgstr ""
"Če želite omogočiti to funkcijo, izberite celico(e), ki jo želite "
"spremljati, in izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Podatki</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Veljavnost...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. To bo "
"prikazalo pogovorno okno &sheets; <guilabel>Veljavnost</guilabel>, ki ima "
"tri strani z zavihki."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Criteria</guilabel> page select what type of data is to be "
"considered valid from the <guilabel>Allow:</guilabel> combo box list then "
"define the valid range of values by choosing one of the options in the "
"<guilabel>Data:</guilabel> combo box and entering suitable value(s) into one "
"or both of the edit box(es)."
msgstr ""
"Na strani <guilabel>Merila</guilabel> izberite vrsto podatkov, ki se bodo "
"šteli za veljavne, s seznama kombiniranega polja <guilabel>Dovoli:</"
"guilabel>, nato pa določite veljaven obseg vrednosti tako, da izberete eno "
"od možnosti v <guilabel>Podatki:</guilabel> kombinirano polje in vnos "
"ustreznih vrednosti v eno ali obe polji za urejanje."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:528
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you have done this change to the <guilabel>Error Alert</guilabel> tab. "
"Here you can choose the type of message box (<guimenuitem>Stop</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Warning</guimenuitem> or "
"<guimenuitem>Information</guimenuitem>) that will appear when an invalid "
"value is entered, and define the message box title and message text."
msgstr ""
"Ko naredite to spremembo na zavihku <guilabel>Opozorilo o napaki</guilabel>. "
"Tukaj lahko izberete vrsto sporočilnega polja (<guimenuitem>Ustavi</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Opozorilo</guimenuitem> ali "
"<guimenuitem>Informacije</guimenuitem>), ki se prikaže, ko vnesete "
"neveljavno vrednost, in določite naslov sporočilnega polja in besedilo "
"sporočila."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that this feature only checks data that you enter into the cell, for a "
"way of checking the results from formulae cells see the <link linkend="
"\"formatdata\">Conditional Cell Attributes</link> section of this Handbook."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da ta funkcija preverja le podatke, ki jih vnesete v celico, za "
"način preverjanja rezultatov iz celic formul glejte razdelek <link linkend="
"\"formatdata\">Pogojni atributi celice</link> v tem priročniku."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid "Protection"
msgstr "Zaščita"

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:544
#, no-c-format
msgid "Document Protection"
msgstr "Zaščita dokumentov"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Protecting the document means that without the password a user cannot add or "
"delete sheets. Document protection does not protect cells."
msgstr ""
"Zaščita dokumenta pomeni, da brez gesla uporabnik ne more dodajati ali "
"brisati listov. Zaščita dokumentov ne ščiti celic."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Protect Document...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> A dialog appears asking you for a password. The "
"<guilabel>Password:</guilabel> strength meter indicates if your password is "
"secure enough. The longer the indicator is, the more secure your password."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zaščiti "
"dokument ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> Pojavi se pogovorno okno, ki vas "
"vpraša za geslo. Merilnik moči <guilabel>Geslo:</guilabel> kaže, ali je vaše "
"geslo dovolj varno. Daljši kot je indikator, varnejše je vaše geslo."

#. Tag: phrase
#: advanced.docbook:558
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Protect Document dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno Zaščiti dokument"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:562
#, no-c-format
msgid "That password will then be required to unprotect the document."
msgstr "To geslo bo nato potrebno za odstranitev zaščite dokumenta."

#. Tag: phrase
#: advanced.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Unprotect Document dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno Odstrani zaščito dokumenta"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:573
#, no-c-format
msgid "When a document is protected, you may not:"
msgstr "Ko je dokument zaščiten, ne smete:"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:575
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rename a sheet"
msgstr "Preimenovati lista"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:578
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert a sheet"
msgstr "Vstaviti list"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:581
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove a sheet"
msgstr "Odstrani list"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:584
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide a sheet"
msgstr "Skrij list"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show a sheet"
msgstr "Pokazati lista"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:590
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the sheet properties"
msgstr "Ogledati si lastnosti lista"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:593
#, no-c-format
msgid "Merge or dissociate cells"
msgstr "Združiti ali ločiti celice"

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:600
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sheet protection"
msgstr "Zaščita lista"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Protecting a sheet means protecting the contents of all protected cells and "
"objects on a sheet. Individual cells or a selection of cells can be "
"unprotected within a protected sheet, see <link linkend=\"cell-protection"
"\">next section</link>."
msgstr ""
"Zaščita lista pomeni zaščito vsebine vseh zaščitenih celic in predmetov na "
"listu. Posamezne celice ali izbor celic je mogoče nezaščititi znotraj "
"zaščitenega lista, glejte <link linkend=\"cell-protection\">naslednji "
"razdelek</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:605
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To protect a sheet, select <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Protect Sheet...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. A dialog "
"appears asking you for a password. The <guilabel>Password</guilabel> "
"strength meter indicates if your password is secure enough. The longer the "
"indicator is, the more secure will be your password."
msgstr ""
"Če želite zaščititi list, izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Zaščiti list...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Prikaže se "
"pogovorno okno, ki vas vpraša za geslo. Merilnik moči <guilabel>gesla</"
"guilabel> kaže, ali je vaše geslo dovolj varno. Daljši kot je indikator, "
"varnejše bo vaše geslo."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:610
#, no-c-format
msgid "That password will then be required to unprotect the sheet."
msgstr "To geslo bo nato potrebno za odstranitev zaščite lista."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid "When a sheet is protected, you may not:"
msgstr "Ko je list zaščiten, ne smete:"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:613
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert any object or chart"
msgstr "Vstaviti poljuben predmet ali grafikon"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid "Format any cell"
msgstr "Oblikovati poljubno celico"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:619
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert a row or a column"
msgstr "Vstaviti vrstico ali stolpec"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:622
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit and change cell content"
msgstr "Urejati in spreminjati vsebine celice"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:625
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change any content in the sheet"
msgstr "Spreminjati poljubno vsebino na listu"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:630
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Protecting a sheet is especially useful for preventing accidental erasure of "
"formulae."
msgstr ""
"Zaščita lista je še posebej uporabna za preprečevanje nenamernega brisanja "
"formul."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:635
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cell or selected cells protection"
msgstr "Zaščita celice ali izbranih celic"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:636
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cell protection is active for all cells by default and is effective when you "
"enable sheet protection. So if you keep the default and if you protect the "
"sheet, all cells will be protected."
msgstr ""
"Zaščita celic je privzeto aktivna za vse celice in deluje, ko omogočite "
"zaščito lista. Torej, če obdržite privzeto in če zaščitite list, bodo vse "
"celice zaščitene."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:639
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want only certain cells to be protected, this default protection must "
"be turned off for all other cells. For example you might want most cells to "
"accept user input so you will uncheck <guilabel>Protected</guilabel> for "
"those and choose to keep protected cells that should stay unchanged (such as "
"titles). So you need 3 steps in order to protect only some cells: unprotect "
"all the cells, select the cells to protect and protect them and then protect "
"the whole sheet."
msgstr ""
"Če želite, da so zaščitene le določene celice, mora biti ta privzeta zaščita "
"izklopljena za vse druge celice. Morda boste na primer želeli, da večina "
"celic sprejme uporabniški vnos, zato boste pri njih počistili polje "
"<guilabel>Zaščiteno</guilabel> in se odločili, da obdržite zaščitene celice, "
"ki naj ostanejo nespremenjene (kot so naslovi). Torej potrebujete 3 korake, "
"da zaščitite samo nekatere celice: odstranite zaščito vseh celic, izberite "
"celice, ki jih želite zaščititi in zaščitite, nato pa zaščitite celoten list."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:646
#, no-c-format
msgid "To unprotect all the cells:"
msgstr "Za odstranitev zaščite vseh celic:"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:648
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the entire spreadsheet with the mouse."
msgstr "Z miško izberite celotno preglednico."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:651
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the menubar, select <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Cell Format...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"V menijski vrstici izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Oblika</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Oblika celice ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:655 advanced.docbook:675
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the dialog that appears, go to the <guilabel>Cell Protection</guilabel> "
"tab."
msgstr ""
"V pogovornem oknu, ki se prikaže, pojdite na zavihek <guilabel>Zaščita "
"celice</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:658
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check <guilabel>Hide all</guilabel> and uncheck <guilabel>Protected</"
"guilabel> to remove the protection on all cells. The cells are now all "
"unprotected."
msgstr ""
"Označite <guilabel>Skrij vse</guilabel> in počistite polje "
"<guilabel>Zaščiteno</guilabel>, da odstranite zaščito vseh celic. Celice so "
"zdaj vse nezaščitene."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:663
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To protect a range of selected cells or a selection of non-contiguous cells:"
msgstr "Če želite zaščititi obseg izbranih celic ali izbor nesosednjih celic:"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:666
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Highlight the range of cells that are to be protected or use the <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;</keycombo> key to select non-contiguous cells."
msgstr ""
"Označite obseg celic, ki jih želite zaščititi, ali uporabite tipko <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;</keycombo>, da izberete nesosednje celice."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:670
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When all of the desired cells are selected, go to the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guimenuitem>Cell Format...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu."
msgstr ""
"Ko so izbrane vse želene celice, pojdite v meni <menuchoice><guimenu>Oblika</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Oblika celice...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:678
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the box next to <guilabel>Protected</guilabel> then click on "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite polje zraven <guilabel>Zaščiteno</guilabel> in kliknite "
"<guibutton>V redu</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once the cells are marked for protection, the protection option must be "
"enabled at the sheet level, that means you must protect the entire sheet for "
"the cell to be effectively protected:"
msgstr ""
"Ko so celice označene za zaščito, mora biti možnost zaščite omogočena na "
"ravni lista, kar pomeni, da morate zaščititi celoten list, da bo celica "
"učinkovito zaščitena:"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:687
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Protect Sheet...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zaščiti list...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:691
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the dialog that appears, provide a safe password, then confirm it by "
"typing it again. Click on <guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"V pogovornem oknu, ki se prikaže, vnesite varno geslo in ga potrdite tako, "
"da ga znova vnesete. Kliknite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:695
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Protected cells in a protected sheet cannot be edited without unprotecting "
"the whole sheet, and any sheet changes are disabled. For example, no one can "
"insert rows or columns, change column width, or create embedded charts."
msgstr ""
"Zaščitenih celic na zaščitenem listu ni mogoče urejati, ne da bi odstranili "
"zaščito celotnega lista, vse spremembe lista pa so onemogočene. Nihče na "
"primer ne more vstaviti vrstic ali stolpcev, spremeniti širine stolpcev ali "
"ustvariti vdelanih grafikonov."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:704
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide cell formula"
msgstr "Skrij celično formulo"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You might want to hide your formulae so other people cannot see them. By "
"default, every cell is protected and not hidden. But it is important to "
"remember that these attributes have no effect unless the sheet itself is "
"protected."
msgstr ""
"Morda boste želeli svoje formule skriti, da jih drugi ljudje ne bodo videli. "
"Privzeto je vsaka celica zaščitena in ni skrita. Pomembno pa si je "
"zapomniti, da ti atributi nimajo učinka, razen če je sam list zaščiten."

#. Tag: phrase
#: advanced.docbook:715
#, no-c-format
msgid "A default cell with a formula"
msgstr "Privzeta celica s formulo"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:719
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To hide cell formulae, select the appropriate cell or range of cells or non-"
"contiguous cells with <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;</keycombo> and then "
"choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guimenuitem>Cell Format...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu. In the Cell format dialog, click the "
"<guilabel>Cell Protection</guilabel> tab and select <guilabel>Hide formula</"
"guilabel>. After you protect the sheet, the results of the formulae will be "
"visible, but the formulae will not."
msgstr ""
"Če želite skriti celične formule, izberite ustrezno celico ali obseg celic "
"ali nesosednjih celic s <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;</keycombo> in nato "
"izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Oblika</guimenu><guimenuitem >Meni Oblika "
"celice ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. V pogovornem oknu Oblika celice "
"kliknite zavihek <guilabel>Zaščita celice</guilabel> in izberite "
"<guilabel>Skrij formulo</guilabel>. Ko zaščitite list, bodo rezultati formul "
"vidni, formule pa ne."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:726
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You have now to protect the sheet: choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Protect Sheet...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to display "
"the <guilabel>Protect Sheet</guilabel> dialog box. Enter a safe password "
"twice to prevent others from unprotecting the sheet."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj morate zaščititi list: izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Zaščiti list ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da se "
"prikaže pogovorno okno <guilabel>Zaščiti list</guilabel> . Dvakrat vnesite "
"varno geslo, da drugim preprečite odstranitev zaščite lista."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:730
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When <guilabel>Hide formula</guilabel> is enabled and <guilabel>Protected</"
"guilabel> is disabled, the formula is hidden after protecting the sheet but "
"the cell content can be changed."
msgstr ""
"Ko je <guilabel>Skrij formulo</guilabel> omogočeno in <guilabel>Zaščiteno</"
"guilabel> onemogočeno, je formula po zaščiti lista skrita, vendar je vsebino "
"celice mogoče spremeniti."

#. Tag: phrase
#: advanced.docbook:739
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Hide formula</guilabel> is enabled but the cell is not protected "
"and the sheet is protected"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Skrij formulo</guilabel> je omogočeno, vendar celica ni zaščitena "
"in list je zaščiten"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:744
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When <guilabel>Hide formula</guilabel> and <guilabel>Protected</guilabel> "
"are enabled, the formula is hidden after protecting the sheet and the cell "
"content cannot be changed."
msgstr ""
"Ko sta <guilabel>Skrij formulo</guilabel> in <guilabel>Zaščiteno</guilabel> "
"omogočeni, je formula po zaščiti lista skrita in vsebine celice ni mogoče "
"spremeniti."

#. Tag: phrase
#: advanced.docbook:753
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Hide formula</guilabel> and <guilabel>Protected</guilabel> are "
"enabled in <guilabel>Cell Protection</guilabel> and the sheet is protected"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Skrij formulo</guilabel> in <guilabel>Zaščiteno</guilabel> sta "
"omogočena v <guilabel>Zaščiti celic</guilabel> in list je zaščiten"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:758
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Keep in mind that it is very easy to break the password for a protected "
"sheet so if you are looking for real security, this is not the best solution."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da je geslo za zaščiten list zelo enostavno zlomiti, tako da, "
"če iščete resnično varnost, to ni najboljša rešitev."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:764
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide all in the cell"
msgstr "Skrij vse v celici"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:765
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can hide both the formula and the content of the cell by choosing "
"<guilabel>Hide all</guilabel> in the Cell Protection tab in the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guimenuitem>Cell Format...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu. In the screenshot below, the cell itself is "
"not protected (<guilabel>Protected</guilabel> is unchecked) thus the cell "
"content can be changed."
msgstr ""
"Formulo in vsebino celice lahko skrijete tako, da izberete <guilabel>Skrij "
"vse</guilabel> na zavihku Zaščita celice v <menuchoice><guimenu>Oblika</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Oblika celice ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> meni. Na "
"spodnjem posnetku zaslona sama celica ni zaščitena (<guilabel>Zaščiteno</"
"guilabel> ni označeno), zato je vsebino celice mogoče spremeniti."

#. Tag: phrase
#: advanced.docbook:777
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Hide all</guilabel> only is enabled (no cell protection) and the "
"sheet is protected"
msgstr ""
"Omogočeno je samo <guilabel>Skrij vse</guilabel> (brez zaščite celice) in "
"list je zaščiten"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:782
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here the cell itself is protected so it cannot be overwritten."
msgstr "Tukaj je sama celica zaščitena, tako da je ni mogoče prepisati."

#. Tag: phrase
#: advanced.docbook:789
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Hide all</guilabel> and <guilabel>Protected</guilabel> are enabled "
"in Cell Protection and the sheet is protected"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Skrij vse</guilabel> in <guilabel>Zaščiteno</guilabel> sta "
"omogočeni v zaščiti celice in list je zaščiten"

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:799
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other Features"
msgstr "Druge funkcije"

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:828
#, no-c-format
msgid "Named Cells and Areas"
msgstr "Imenovane celice in območja"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:829
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can give a name such as <userinput>foo</userinput> to a cell or to any "
"area of a sheet by selecting the cell or area then selecting <guimenuitem> "
"Area Name...</guimenuitem> from the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse "
"button menu. This will bring up the <guilabel>Area Name</guilabel> dialog "
"box where you can enter any name you wish."
msgstr ""
"Celici ali kateremu koli območju lista lahko daste ime, kot je "
"<userinput>foo</userinput>, tako da izberete celico ali območje in nato "
"izberete <guimenuitem> Ime področja...</guimenuitem> iz <mousebutton> desni</"
"mousebutton> meni gumba miške. To bo prikazalo pogovorno okno <guilabel>Ime "
"območja</guilabel>, kjer lahko vnesete poljubno ime."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:834
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also name a cell or area by selecting it then typing the name into "
"the small text box at the left end of the Formula toolbar, overwriting the "
"cell reference that normally appears here."
msgstr ""
"Celico ali območje lahko poimenujete tudi tako, da ga izberete in nato "
"vnesete ime v majhno polje z besedilom na levem koncu orodne vrstice "
"Formule, s čimer prepišete referenco celice, ki se običajno pojavi tukaj."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:837
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you enter a name that has already been used into this text box &sheets;'s "
"selection will change to show the named cell(s)."
msgstr ""
"Če v to besedilno polje vnesete ime, ki je že bilo uporabljeno, se bo izbor "
"&sheets; spremenil in prikazal poimenovane celice."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:839
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <menuchoice><guimenu>Data</guimenu><guimenuitem>Named Areas...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> option will give you a list of existing names and "
"let you change &sheets;'s focus to any of them or let you remove a name."
msgstr ""
"Možnost <menuchoice><guimenu>Podatki</guimenu><guimenuitem>Poimenovana "
"območja ...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> vam bo ponudila seznam obstoječih "
"imen in vam omogočila, da spremenite žarišče &sheets; na katero koli od njih "
"ali dovoli, da odstranite ime."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:843
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Named cells are particularly useful in formulae as an alternative to <link "
"linkend=\"absolute\"> absolute cell references</link> as the names can be "
"used in place of normal cell references and do not change when the cell "
"containing the formula is copied. When a name is used in this way it should "
"be enclosed in single quotation marks."
msgstr ""
"Poimenovane celice so še posebej uporabne v formulah kot alternativa <link "
"linkend=\"absolute\"> absolutnim sklicem na celice</link>, saj je mogoče "
"imena uporabiti namesto običajnih sklicev na celice in se ne spremenijo, ko "
"je celica, ki vsebuje formulo, kopirana . Če je ime uporabljeno na ta način, "
"mora biti v enojnih narekovajih."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:848
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example, if cell A1 has been given the name <userinput>fred </userinput> "
"then you can enter a formula such as <userinput>='fred' + 2 </userinput> "
"into another cell which would always give the result of adding 2 to the "
"value in A1 no matter where the formula cell was copied to."
msgstr ""
"Na primer, če je celica A1 dobila ime <userinput>fred </userinput>, potem "
"lahko v drugo celico vnesete formulo, kot je <userinput>='fred' + 2 </"
"userinput>, ki bi vedno dala rezultat dodajanje 2 vrednosti v A1 ne glede na "
"to, kam je bila celica s formulo kopirana."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:852
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note that cell and area names are treated as being in lowercase."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da se imena celic in območij obravnavajo kot napisana z malimi "
"črkami."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:856
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cell Comments"
msgstr "Komentarji celice"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:857
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A cell can contain a text comment that can be viewed when working on the "
"spreadsheet but which is not printed and not normally seen."
msgstr ""
"Celica lahko vsebuje besedilni komentar, ki si ga lahko ogledate med delom "
"na preglednici, vendar ni natisnjen in običajno ni viden."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:859
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add a comment select the cell and choose <guimenuitem>Comment...</"
"guimenuitem> from the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse button menu or "
"from the <guimenu>Insert</guimenu> menu and type your comment into the "
"resulting <guilabel>Cell Comment</guilabel> dialog box."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati komentar, izberite celico in izberite "
"<guimenuitem>Komentar...</guimenuitem> v meniju <mousebutton>desnega</"
"mousebutton> gumba miške ali v meniju <guimenu>Vstavi</guimenu> in vnesite "
"svoj komentar v nastalo pogovorno okno <guilabel>Komentar celice</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:863
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To see the comment hover the mouse pointer over the cell. The comment will "
"appear as if it were a Tooltip."
msgstr ""
"Če želite videti komentar, premaknite miškin kazalec nad celico. Komentar bo "
"prikazan kot opis orodja."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:866
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check the <guilabel>Show comment indicator</guilabel> box of the "
"<guilabel>Sheet Properties</guilabel> dialog, those cells containing "
"comments will be highlighted by a small red triangle in the top right corner."
msgstr ""
"Če označite polje <guilabel>Pokaži indikator komentarja</guilabel> v "
"pogovornem oknu <guilabel>Lastnosti lista</guilabel>, bodo tiste celice, ki "
"vsebujejo komentarje, označene z majhnim rdečim trikotnikom v zgornjem "
"desnem kotu."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:870
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To open this dialog, click with the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse "
"button onto the sheet tab at the bottom of the main window and select "
"<guimenuitem>Sheet Properties</guimenuitem> from the popup menu. Or select "
"it from the <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guisubmenu>Sheet</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> menu."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odpreti to pogovorno okno, kliknite z <mousebutton>desno</"
"mousebutton> miškino tipko na zavihek lista na dnu glavnega okna in v "
"pojavnem meniju izberite <guimenuitem>Lastnosti lista</guimenuitem>. Ali pa "
"ga izberite v meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Oblika</guimenu><guisubmenu>List</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:875
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove a comment from a cell, select <guimenuitem>Remove Comment</"
"guimenuitem> from the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse button menu or "
"choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guisubmenu>Clear</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Comment</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odstraniti komentar iz celice, izberite <guimenuitem>Odstrani "
"komentar</guimenuitem> v meniju <mousebutton>desnega</mousebutton> gumba "
"miške ali izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guisubmenu>Počisti</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Komentar</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
